---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Operating System Architecture — Wychwood Partners" description="Design and install capital-disciplined operating system architecture for growth-stage and PE-backed businesses.">
  <main class="shell py-14">
    <h1>Operating System Architecture</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))]">
      An institutional operating system that aligns ownership, decision rights, capital discipline, and performance governance across growth-stage and private equity-backed businesses.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))]">
      This is the structural layer that connects strategy, unit economics, and execution cadence — without adding bureaucracy.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="card p-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold">What it includes</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))]">
          <li>• Multi-layer metrics hierarchy (team → executive → board)</li>
          <li>• Unit economics governance and variance thresholds</li>
          <li>• Decision rights and escalation architecture</li>
          <li>• Weekly execution cadence tied to capital allocation</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold">When it’s needed</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))]">
          <li>• Scaling beyond founder-led execution</li>
          <li>• Margin erosion or performance variance</li>
          <li>• Board-level visibility gaps</li>
          <li>• Multi-site or multi-market expansion</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Outcomes</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))]">
          <li>• Board-ready performance visibility</li>
          <li>• Clear capital allocation discipline</li>
          <li>• Faster decision cycles</li>
          <li>• Predictable execution across teams</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 card p-8">
      <p class="text-lg font-semibold">Assess your operating system architecture</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[rgb(var(--text-muted))]">
        In 30 minutes we’ll identify where governance, capital discipline, and execution cadence are breaking down — and define the structural fixes required.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="mt-5 inline-flex rounded-[var(--radius-lg)] bg-[rgb(var(--brand-anchor))] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white transition hover:opacity-95">Book a call</a>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
